{% set notes %}
{% spaceless %}
  <bolt-ol>
    <bolt-li>The Table Basic component is designed to work with both Twig and vanilla HTML (Twig is the recommended method).</bolt-li>
    <bolt-li>Refer to the <a href="{{ link['components-table-basic-top-header'] }}" class="e-bolt-text-link">Table Basic with Top Header</a> page for information on adding a top header.</bolt-li>
    <bolt-li>Refer to the <a href="{{ link['components-table-basic-side-header'] }}" class="e-bolt-text-link">Table Basic with Side Header</a> page for information on adding a side header.</bolt-li>
    <bolt-li><strong>HTML:</strong> To align the table columns correctly, include a <code>&lt;td&gt;</code> to the <code>&lt;thead&gt;</code> as the first cell.</bolt-li>
  </bolt-ol>
{% endspaceless %}
{% endset %}

